                                  Aquatics
   [green_white_right.gif]
   St. Lucie County Parks & Recreation invites you to take a swim. We
   offer a variety of activities at our pools such as lap swim,
   instructional classes, water exercise and open swim. We also rent our
   pools for private parties.

   Aquatics Safety Coordinator - (561) 462-1961


